)|Jordan Black]]\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|5|7}}\n |Viewers         = 0.82<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-tuesday-cable-originals-network-finals-5-7-2019.html|title=Updated: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Tuesday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 5.7.2019|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=May 8, 2019|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=May 8, 2019}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    =\n |LineColor       = 2E516C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 17\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 7\n |Title           = Criminal Minded\n |DirectedBy      = [[Reginald Hudlin]]\n |WrittenBy       = Arthur Harris & [[Angela Nissel]]\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|5|14}}\n |Viewers         = 0.74<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-tuesday-cable-originals-network-finals-5-14-2019.html|title=Updated: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Tuesday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 5.14.2019|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=May 15, 2019|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=May 15, 2019}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    =\n |LineColor       = 2E516C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 18\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 8\n |Title           = Mama Said Knock You Out\n |DirectedBy      = Maurice Marable\n |WrittenBy       = Tracey Ashley\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|5|21}}\n |Viewers         = 0.97<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-tuesday-cable-originals-network-finals-5-21-2019.html|title=Updated: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Tuesday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 5.21.2019|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=May 22, 2019|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=May 22, 2019}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = 2E516C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 19\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 9\n |Title           = Your Mom's in My Business\n |DirectedBy      = Reginald Hudlin\n |WrittenBy       = Jordan Black\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|5|28}}\n |Viewers         = 0.93<ref>{{cite web|url=http